<list_item><loc_98><loc_375><loc_436><loc_391>To augment the non-teaching  personnel  requirements  of schools, the following  measures  may be implemented:</list_item>
<list_item><loc_113><loc_397><loc_436><loc_420>SDOs may cluster deployed non-teaching  personnel  in accordance with the deployment  Patameters  issued by the Bureau of Human Resource and Organizational  Development (BHROD); and</list_item>
