<section_header_level_1><loc_54><loc_412><loc_234><loc_421>VI. MONITORING A]TD EVALUATIOil</section_header_level_1>
<text><loc_82><loc_429><loc_436><loc_443><loc_80><loc_51><loc_433><loc_65>The Department  of Education,  through the BHROD,  shall monitor, evaluate, and review the implementation  of this policy. Furthermore, BHROD-SED  shall gather feedback on the implementation of these guidelines from concemed  personnel across different  govemance  levels.</text>
