<section_header_level_1><loc_53><loc_190><loc_197><loc_199>IX. TRANSITORYPROVISION</section_header_level_1>
<text><loc_81><loc_205><loc_435><loc_228>To ensure the smooth and effective implementation of this Order, the SDOs shall immediately implement  the following within a period not exceeding sixty (60) calendar days:</text>
